00:40:10,447 --> 00:40:17,267
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The way back home is long</font>

294
00:40:18,127 --> 00:40:24,417
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}but I promised to come here again tomorrow</font>

295
00:40:28,167 --> 00:40:40,447
